---
title: Griddled Onion Cheeseburgers with Special Sauce & Garlic Broccoli Florets
description: Is there anything more satisfying than a cheeseburger? (Don’t worry, we checked, and the answer was a resounding “no!”) There is a difference, however, between a good cheeseburger and a great one. After you try a bite of ours, we know you’ll agree that this one falls in the GREAT category. Juicy beef patties are topped with melty cheddar, sweet griddled onion, ripe tomato slices, and finally, special sauce. You’ll want to put that sauce on everything, but it’s especially awesome on the side with our crispy potato wedges.
